title: Joe Satriani-Surfing With The Alien   FLAC        ak6103
description: Joe Satriani-Surfing With The Alien 1987  FLAC  What we got Some of the Premier guitarwork from a true innovator and when you listen remember that this was back in the 80's true late 80's but still and Im gonna enjoy it to I used to party back when this was new and the satchman used to have an affinity for Sonoma County CA. so he would play at a Venue Called The Luthor Burbank Center in Santa Rosa about at least once or twice a year which was about 50 miles from the pad so Im fortunate to have seen him when this was new, amazing.  Anyway here it is good and lossless just the way it should be. if you want get it, If you keep please help seed so others can be amazed thanks..........
